Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.58,0:01:41.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They are kept at a distance...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.25,0:01:44.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Coarse and mysterious...\NThey seem to be completely different{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:47.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}from the flora and fauna\nthat are familiar to us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:50.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This group of strange looking creatures{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.53,0:01:53.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}has inflicted fear onto humans\nsince long past,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.27,0:01:58.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and have come to be called... "mushi".{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:32.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sui.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:36.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Biki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:48.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:51.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do your eyes still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:52.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Biki...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:54.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:57.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you in on a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:03:02.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know... what's causing my disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:07.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's a {\i1}mushi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:12.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,living in there... all this time...\ninside my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:18.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sui is the youngest daughter\nof the head family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:20.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About a half a year ago,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:24.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she contracted a disease\nwhich made her eyes sensitive to light.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:33.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}None of the eye doctors could find\nthe cause of her strange illness,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and before they could even\nfigure out a course of treatment,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:39.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}her eyes became so sensitized that even\na little light began to cause her great pain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:48.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As a result, she was left with our family{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:51.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}since we have a sturdy storage shed\nwhich blocks out light.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:54.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although it may have been\nfor Sui's own good,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:59.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it appeared to me that she\nwas abandoned at our house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:18.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's another eyelid behind my eyelid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:27.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a place where outside light\ncan never get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:29.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's where the {\i1}mushi{\i0} live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:32.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A second eyelid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:34.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.22,0:04:36.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know how to\nclose your second eyelid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:38.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll teach you how.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:39.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:41.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:44.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:46.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:48.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:56.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I do see some flickering\nmovements within my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:05:01.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You see? Even after you close your eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:04.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,your eyes are still looking\nat the backs of your eyelids...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:06.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,so they're not really closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.86,0:05:13.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, whenever I want it pitch-black,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:18.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I close my eyes again to\nthose flickering movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:26.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's when a curtain\nof true darkness falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:42.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:46.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You're so uncoordinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:02.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We play in the deep darkness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:09.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although I can't see anything\nwhen I first step into the shed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.52,0:06:15.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}after a while, the outlines of things\nstart to gradually appear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:26.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How can you see the ball\nwhen it's pitch black?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:30.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's because there is a river of light\nrunning under the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:32.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:36.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can see it if you\nclose your second eyelid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.21,0:06:39.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When I keep staring at true darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:45.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...from afar, tiny specks\nof light start appearing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:48.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and they rapidly form into a river.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:55.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When I look at the light carefully, I can\nsee that it's all made up of tiny {\i1}mushi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:07:00.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But when I try to go closer\nto get a better look...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:03.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:14.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get any closer to that river.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:17.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a man I've never met before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:24.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A man with one eye is always on the\nother side of the river saying that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:29.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I just look\nat the river from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:30.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:35.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}... sometimes become uneasy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:58.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those things that Sui sees with\nher eyes closed... what on earth...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:05.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What on earth can they be?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:14.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Biki! You spend way too much time\ninside the storage shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:17.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I disposed of all the used\neye bandages by burning them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:20.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I disinfected my hands\nand all the eating utensils, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:29.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Still... there's no guarantee\nthat you won't get infected, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:34.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The head family had the same fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they abandoned Sui, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:39.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:43.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:46.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sui's a good girl. A very good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:49.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:09:02.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keep supporting her so that she doesn't\nlose the light in her heart as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:07.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:11.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,don't get infected with\nthat disease like she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:16.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:22.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:24.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...coming here for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:18.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:21.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:26.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:31.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be... Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:58.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Biki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:00.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:04.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Biki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:17.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Biki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:22.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Biki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:28.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Biki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:36.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...won't be allowed to come here any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:39.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's caught your illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:51.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not... your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:56.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's our fault for taking pity on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:18.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there? If you leave\nthe storm door open, Biki will!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:20.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:25.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am an expert in these matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:31.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I applied medicine and some painkiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:35.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving him in the dark will only\nmake the disease progress further.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:38.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:40.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:44.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ginko. I am a mushi-shi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:48.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I caught wind of the girl\nin your storage shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:55.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Her disease is something that\ncan't be cured by an eye doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:12:57.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but by a mushi-shi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:01.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Will Biki... will my son be cured?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.87,0:13:06.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the {\i1}mushi{\i0} he has\nseems to be a newborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:10.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So treatment with medicine alone\nwill probably be effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:20.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Biki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:25.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Biki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:29.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Biki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:35.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:39.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:41.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:43.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sui!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:53.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're awake now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:58.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do your eyes still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.26,0:14:01.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:04.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good. The medicine worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:09.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The cause of Sui's illness is\nthe Manako Yami {\i1}mushi.\N(Manako{\i0} = {\i1}eye, Yami{\i0} = {\i1}darkness){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:12.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They multiply in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:19.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You spent too much time\nwith Sui in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:22.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You know Sui?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:25.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's one-eyed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I closed my second eyelid,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:30.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,she was on the opposite bank of the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:31.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:36.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That river of light is comprised of\na different element from earthly light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:40.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's harmful to your eyes\nif you look at it too closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:42.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He has his other eye.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:46.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if he's a different person\nfrom the one Sui mentioned...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:51.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start Sui's treatment\nafter the sun sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:55.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.25,0:14:56.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:20.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sui!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:23.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:26.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After I told you so many times\nnot to go into the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:42.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sui...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:16:01.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sui's eyeballs are already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:02.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.18,0:16:05.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll try something anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:08.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you close your second eyelid\nfor too long,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.85,0:16:11.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,your eyeball gets eaten by the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:15.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, ready, Sui?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:17.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to lure out\nthe {\i1}mushi{\i0} with the moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:24.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,While keeping your second eyelid closed,\nslowly open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:48.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, {\i1}mushi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.56,0:16:50.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's light out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:14.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}M-mushi!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:27.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:30.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sui, that's enough. Close your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:59.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:03.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now... let's take a look at Sui's eyeballs...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:08.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}M-mushi!{\i0} There really\nwas a {\i1}mushi{\i0} in Sui's eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.51,0:18:13.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought, her eyes\nare no longer functioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:15.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if this will work, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:25.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give this to Sui.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:28.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you've been overreacting\nfor a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.53,0:18:33.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't freak out so much. It's a glass eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:35.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is the liquid {\i1}mushi{\i0}\nthat you saw earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:41.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I inject this into a glass ball,\nit should turn into a functioning eyeball.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:51.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:55.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That river of light that you both can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.22,0:18:57.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is it anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:19:01.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Try closing your second eyelid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:06.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:11.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then the path to darkness will be revealed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:16.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, you too were\nwatching it, just like us...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:29.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From the time a person\nopens his eyes to the light,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:33.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he is said to have forgotten\nhow to close his second eyelid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:42.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, it was perhaps\nfor the better to those living,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:46.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}for before that time, it is said\nthat many had lost their eyesight{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:50.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}from staring too much at the river of light.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:20:03.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The second eyelid,\ntrue darkness, alien light...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:19.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The group of infinite life forms\nswimming beneath our feet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:29.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All around us became really bright and\nright after, we were plunged into darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.25,0:20:37.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The ground fell out beneath me and\NI saw a river of light flowing way below.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:41.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It just happened for a split second
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:45.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,after that {\i1}mushi-shi-san{\i0}\nput the glass eye into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:51.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But it was so pretty and I felt as though\nmy body was being pulled into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:53.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to stare at it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:00.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:07.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sui came out of the shed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:12.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She looks a lot at the trees\nand flowers and light.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.22,0:21:19.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She will probably never be lured\nby that strange light in the darkness again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:29.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if that mushi-shi lost his real eye\nin the same way Sui did...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:34.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"The Light of the Eyelid"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.56,0:23:38.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"The Tender Horns"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.23,0:23:43.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Mushi-shi"\N"Look forward to the next episode."
